      "writtenOn": "2021-05-20T06:18:32Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "As long as the file is not broken, files should not be downloaded again (see \"verify\" function in this file).\n\nBut I see your point. In my suggested approach downloaded files are verified again and again per fixture/test runs. This can be costly for large files as we compute file content hash.\n\nSo the current approach sounds good to me. Thanks for explanation!",
